Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Thoracic CT
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Characterization' tab

When I select 'Decreased parenchymal density' from Finding dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding button' is enabled

When I select 'Decreased parenchymal density' from Finding dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding button' is enabled
And 'Honey combing' radio button is enabled
And 'Microcystic honeycombing' radio button is enabled
And 'Cysts' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Cysts' radio button
Then 'Air filled' radio button is enabled
And 'Liquid-filled' radio button is enabled
And 'Thin-walled' radio button is enabled
And 'Thick-walled' radio button is enabled
